---
<section class="hero">
    <h1>Welcome to the Official Homepage of John Blanchard Jefferson's Books</h1>
    <p>Master of Modern Thrillers</p>
    <a href="/books" class="cta">Explore the Books</a>
</section>
  
<style>
.hero {
    background: url('/jefferson.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
    color: white;
    padding: 8rem 1rem;
    text-align: right;
    border: #0033cc 2px solid;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px 5px rgba(0, 51, 204, 0.8);
}

.hero h1 {
    font-size: 2rem; /* Increased font size */
    max-width: 50%; /* Contain the heading to the right side */
    margin-left: auto; /* Push the heading to the right */
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); /* Adds a subtle shadow */
    text-align: center;
  ;

}

.hero p {
    text-shadow: 4px 4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); /* Keeps the shadow */
    text-align: right;

}

.cta {
    background: #cc0000;
    color: white;
    padding: .75rem 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    border-radius: 4px;
    

    
}
</style>
